    "v3": "Jesus comes to hearts rejoicing, Bringing news of sins forgiv&#39;n; Jesus comes in sounds of gladness, Leading souls redeemed to Heav&#39;n; Alleluia! Alleluia! Now the gate of death is riv&#39;n.",
    "v4": "Jesus comes in joy and sorrow, Shares alike our hopes and fears; Jesus comes, whate&#39;er befalls us, Glads our hearts, and dries our tears; Alleluia! Alleluia! Cheering e&#39;en our failing years.",
    "v5": "Jesus comes on clouds triumphant, When the heav&#39;ns shall pass away; Jesus comes again in glory; Let us then our homage pay, Alleluia! Alleluia! Till the dawn of endless day."
  },
